Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十七話 左之助對安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.40,0:01:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人 探子傳來情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.06,0:01:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村、齊藤、相樂\N從葵屋出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.20,0:02:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 召集十本刀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.04,0:02:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來終於要正面決鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.11,0:02:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前\N我要提議一個作戰計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰計劃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.35,0:02:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方治 你到底在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.82,0:02:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想的事只有一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.13,0:02:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是志志雄大人的完全勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.10,0:02:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全勝利？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 這場戰鬥相對於
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.10,0:02:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村、齊藤、相樂三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.04,0:02:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們連同您在內有十個人\N勝利是毫無疑問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.54,0:02:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不就好了  你幹嘛多此一舉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.88,0:02:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是敵人是精銳中的精銳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.15,0:02:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣硬碰硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.65,0:02:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十本刀之中\N確實有些人實力不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.26,0:02:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以  乾脆我們也用精英政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.89,0:02:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從十本刀之中選出前三強\N來對付那三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.66,0:03:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十本刀剩下的六個人\N則去殺死留在葵屋的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都大火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為御庭幫忍者的暗中活動\N（註：江戶德川御用忍者）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而被阻止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是拔刀齊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.31,0:03:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要情報來源、後方支援者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.78,0:03:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說 沒收拾掉他們\N可以說是所有麻煩之源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.52,0:03:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但因此做出偷襲的卑鄙行為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.09,0:03:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別忘了  我們的最終目標是\N掌握這個國家的霸權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.76,0:03:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是志志雄大人的完全勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為此 偷襲是天經地義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.57,0:03:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在同時殺死緋村拔刀齊\N與其同黨才是上上之策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.88,0:03:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何時偉大到\N可以對我提意見了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對拔刀齊說過是決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.55,0:04:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我身為劍客的自信\N不容許我扭曲那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.53,0:04:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決鬥絕不更改\N你立刻去把十本刀叫過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.63,0:04:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自從志志雄大人以那拳頭\N給了我修羅的覺悟後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.24,0:04:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就暗下一個決心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.74,0:04:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了引導志志雄大人\N步上絕對的勝利之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.81,0:04:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要全神投入擬定策略\N加以執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.08,0:04:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝者為王敗者為寇\N歷史是勝利者寫出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.59,0:04:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去煉獄的現在\N我們只剩十本刀這個王牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.96,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浪費這張王牌的策略\N我方治是無論如何不能贊同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.53,0:04:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我發誓要把完全的勝利\N獻給志志雄大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.90,0:04:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為此  不論使用多卑鄙的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.60,0:04:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算為此被人們、被同胞\N甚至被志志雄大人厭惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.84,0:04:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都…我都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都絕不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.45,0:05:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是頭一次受到\N自己養的狗這麼反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.02,0:05:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了  宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.79,0:05:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫十本刀過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決鬥馬上就要開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.70,0:05:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在那之前\N我要先談煉獄的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.04,0:05:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事我也很想問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.47,0:05:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好京都大火只是晃子\N我們被當成棄卒利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.85,0:05:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底是怎麼回事呀\N志志雄大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也感到抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.32,0:05:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實本來應該你們上煉獄\N前往東京的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為方治說是晃子最好顯眼點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.76,0:05:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而在緊要關頭擅自變更計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是這樣啊 方治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.64,0:06:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都是我的責任\N請你們原諒我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.95,0:06:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 我以為是\N志志雄大人拋棄我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.29,0:06:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還大受打擊呢 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可不能平白饒了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.30,0:06:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方治 你說出實話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.43,0:06:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂你講什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.33,0:06:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我的心眼之前\N謊言是行不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.91,0:06:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要說出實話\N你就可以不必受苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.95,0:06:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣 想說了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.39,0:06:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.96,0:06:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只說真話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.93,0:06:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對十本刀七人的背叛\N全是我獨斷獨行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.14,0:07:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.34,0:07:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對志志雄大人的\N不信任與懷疑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.04,0:07:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我願以此自罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.94,0:07:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請把過去的事…付諸水流吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我要發給你們任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.42,0:07:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎、宇水、安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.59,0:07:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們留在這裏\N與拔刀齊他們決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.12,0:07:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他人立刻趕往葵屋\N拿下所有人的人頭過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.66,0:07:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人的人頭嗎  有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的覺悟…我看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後黑臉就給你當了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.75,0:07:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相對的 以後我會\N隨時給你品嚐最高的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待在我的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.92,0:07:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,六連洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.87,0:08:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衝入敵地\N我忍不住興奮得顫抖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.75,0:08:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎 我等您很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.52,0:08:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面是拒絕生者的迷路\N為了避免你們迷路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.09,0:08:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以由小女子我\N駒形由美來領路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.53,0:08:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用女人使人鬆懈大意\N常有這招 小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.63,0:08:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會上這種小當的人頂多只有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.30,0:08:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄不是那種小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.57,0:08:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼請跟我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.78,0:08:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏與其說是迷路\N不如說是迷宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.61,0:08:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走錯一步就可能誤入一堆陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.35,0:08:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了防止外敵的進入\N這麼用盡心思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於決鬥方法  決鬥是一比一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.00,0:09:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們  只留一個人\N在一間房間待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.23,0:09:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也派一個人出來決鬥\N剩下的兩人不可出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這方法怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.81,0:09:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求之不得  打架是一比一最棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.81,0:09:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是怎樣都行\N不過一個個收拾太麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.35,0:09:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的對手不能一齊出來\N讓我一次打倒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生 您呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.25,0:09:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以 但是分出勝負後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.12,0:09:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是有人想致對方於死地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.12,0:09:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論那人是誰\N我都不會坐視不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.56,0:09:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只接受決鬥\N沒答應看人殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.56,0:09:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好天真的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.73,0:09:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.07,0:09:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請恕我多嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分配安慈和尚\N去打相樂左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.47,0:09:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點讓人擔心呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.08,0:09:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教那個男人二重極的人\N不就是和尚自己嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.38,0:10:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們關係那麼深\N誰知道他捨不捨得下殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不用你來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破戒僧再怎樣不守戒律\N終歸是學佛的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.13,0:10:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是十本刀之中最慈悲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.73,0:10:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那男人是被遙遠超越\N慈悲的憤怒而驅使的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.44,0:10:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明王安慈\N不會饒赦妨礙他救世的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是在提升士氣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓自己清醒罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.62,0:10:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我更喜歡去聞\N女人甜甜的血腥味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.72,0:10:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是一樣那麼奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣 安慈 要不要聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.10,0:10:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死志志雄  瓜分他的王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這主意不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你講話是在浪費時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.42,0:11:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 第一人請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.83,0:11:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認識那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.37,0:11:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是教我二重極的破戒僧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.94,0:11:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明王安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.21,0:11:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十本刀的第一位選手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.46,0:11:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走入十本刀這個邪門歪道\N的一位破戒僧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.33,0:11:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有話要問他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一位選手 我接下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.07,0:12:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是救了小操…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.64,0:12:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十本刀的第三高手  明王安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.08,0:12:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道他經歷了什麼事\N總之小心點 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.85,0:12:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他散發的氣勢不可小窺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.72,0:12:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨 一個月不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.09,0:12:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直想再跟你碰面\N可沒想到竟然是以這種形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.53,0:12:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也大感意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.10,0:12:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在下諏訪\N說過絕不原諒明治政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.50,0:12:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來都是騙人謊言\N說實話 我很失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失望的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.61,0:12:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭和尚\N你幫助志志雄的破壞活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的救世到底怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.02,0:12:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒怎麼了\N這個破壞就是救世的第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.35,0:12:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.45,0:12:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著 你可能以為拯救世間\N所有人脫離苦難就是救世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.83,0:13:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前也跟你一樣\N衷心那麼認為 祈盼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.83,0:13:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是現實是不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.87,0:13:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這世間不值得拯救的畜生們\N一副自私嘴臉  貪生怕死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.61,0:13:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而那些人面獸心的\N邪魔歪道奪走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.29,0:13:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該受到拯救的\N心靈清淨的人的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.79,0:13:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是現世的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.53,0:13:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在必需給那些\N不配被拯救的人天譴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.16,0:13:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為此 我才接受委託\N成為十本刀中的明王安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.17,0:13:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給人懲罰的憤怒的化身\N不動明王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.27,0:13:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞世間所有一切 使其歸為無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.11,0:13:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後拯救應拯救的人\N懲罰應懲罰的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.21,0:13:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先使人心再生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.15,0:13:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這才是真的救世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了嗎 相樂左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽不懂啦 光頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.00,0:14:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你不同\N本來就不信什麼神佛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是有一點我很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.94,0:14:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是  我不贊同你的救世觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.88,0:14:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…  煉獄的時候看到的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.38,0:14:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是第三次了  應該不是偶然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.12,0:14:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你算什麼不動明王了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.92,0:14:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一點也不想\N從你口中聽到那句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開下諏訪  到達京都之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.86,0:14:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以百之巖為對手練功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.09,0:14:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如你所見\N學會二重極的究極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.03,0:14:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快投降吧 安慈\N我不想用你教的絕招打你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.37,0:14:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學會究極了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少自大了  小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你學的只是基礎中的基礎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.88,0:14:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個才叫做究極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩手兩足的二重極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.36,0:15:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且左手還是用手肘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實力差別太明顯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.54,0:15:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不贊同我的救世就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.47,0:15:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.01,0:15:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我不會原諒你妨礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.91,0:15:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯  他不只是兩手兩足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.48,0:15:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有心的話 連用頭擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.35,0:15:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都有辦法使出二重極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.72,0:15:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我只會右手\N而且還是正面直拳才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要換人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.99,0:15:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了  事到如今我不能退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.20,0:15:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為你是\N頭腦更聰明的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那這就是你誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.77,0:15:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.27,0:15:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 別膽怯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管腦袋多笨 只要肯思考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.88,0:16:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是可能抓住勝利機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個人都看扁我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.42,0:16:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在劍術上 二刀流的絕招\N不見得勝過一刀的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.39,0:16:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也一樣 有渺茫的勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.99,0:16:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決鬥是一對一\N不能隨便插手的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.53,0:16:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 所以我並沒插手\N只是插插嘴而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那一擊\N讓我看到勝利機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.37,0:16:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝利機會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.61,0:16:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愚蠢 你是沒有那東西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.18,0:16:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有或沒有 試試就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.78,0:16:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如我所料\N他為了練出終極的二重極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過度鍛練肌肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於肌肉過重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.96,0:16:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身法跟不上拳頭的速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二重極的究極是一擊必倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我只有右拳能使出招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先打中的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.34,0:17:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.74,0:17:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.01,0:17:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.58,0:17:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時由正內側加上正拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.68,0:17:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瓦解衝擊的傳導\N緩和那個威力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.19,0:17:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再說一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個才叫做究極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.23,0:17:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好險好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.99,0:17:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到還有\N避開二重極的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.90,0:17:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.83,0:17:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然只是擦過  這個衝擊……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.74,0:17:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣是二重極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然有這麼大差異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.31,0:17:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退吧\N這次我格外施恩饒你一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.94,0:17:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和尚 你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.88,0:17:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得對方都這麼說了\N接受他的好意換人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.22,0:17:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再打下去可就不是開玩笑了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.26,0:17:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 安慈和尚\N這我不能坐視不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人叫你要殺死他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.73,0:18:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少插嘴\N生殺大權是操在我手中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.27,0:18:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說是死是活全看你是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.27,0:18:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼成為明王\N什麼操掌生殺大權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.87,0:18:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙真以為自己是神佛啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.04,0:18:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個權利不是志志雄給你的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.58,0:18:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 志志雄不是\N成為最偉大的佛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.65,0:18:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒接受他的任何給予
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.99,0:18:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是贊同他\N打倒明治政府的理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.32,0:18:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,助他一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果志志雄創造的新時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有違救世之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.20,0:18:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我照樣當他是敵人  打倒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.47,0:18:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算這樣永遠的破壞嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.21,0:18:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂 一點也不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.45,0:18:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我確實痛恨明治政府\N覺得不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.12,0:18:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今仍跟你一樣\N有時忍不住想破壞一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.92,0:18:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.45,0:19:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在明治之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有很多人拚命求生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.69,0:19:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.99,0:19:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而相信未來而戰鬥的\N也是大有人在呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.83,0:19:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要對這個時代感到絕望\N那是你的自由 安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是只要還有人保持希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.57,0:19:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這種\N自以為掌握生殺大權的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.24,0:19:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕不原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.11,0:19:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也絕對不會打輸的 絕對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.11,0:19:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣好吧 再打下去\N他會被打得不成人形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.62,0:19:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前跟左之助打鬥時\N也說過幾乎完全一樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.35,0:19:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 這次他說的不會輸\N份量跟上次不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.60,0:19:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想靠速度取勝也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.10,0:19:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對對方的肌肉鐵壁\N我看他希望渺茫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.14,0:19:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決勝關鍵終究還是那個二重極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,證據是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安慈只把焦點\N放在他的右手上頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.02,0:20:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一點左之助也瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.62,0:20:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從剛才開始\N他一直沒有使出右手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.82,0:20:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了  要為這小鬼\N浪費多少時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.09,0:20:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會當作沒聽見\N剛才的問題發言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快打倒他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.77,0:20:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甘願了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.07,0:20:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說只有右手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.41,0:20:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能在短短一周內\N就學會二重極的基礎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.84,0:20:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要親手殺死你實在略嫌可惜\N但我也別無選擇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.81,0:20:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決鬥時刻  要阻止就要趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.05,0:20:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那麼擔心左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.39,0:20:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是擔心他死了\N你的士氣會下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.36,0:20:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題 左之助不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.70,0:20:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就以自己的身體\N來體會我的救世之正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死後再從黃泉的狹縫間\N觀看我怎樣來救世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.11,0:20:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.41,0:21:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南無阿彌陀佛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.71,0:21:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著 現在念佛還太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二重極被避開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧…安慈和尚被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.05,0:21:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉 贏是贏了\N但好像是湊巧獲勝的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.85,0:21:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對 我發現光靠拳速\N敵不過他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.45,0:21:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而臨時切換身形避開二重極\N這不是賭運氣也不是湊巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.43,0:21:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是相信既然我能\N賭命學會二重極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.30,0:21:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然也就能避開他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.00,0:22:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.97,0:22:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二重極明明直接擊中他的呀

